<SiteLayout site="westmount" title="When Will the $2000 Dividend Be Paid? Understanding Special Dividends" description="Are you waiting for a massive $2000 dividend payment? Find out the crucial dates, who qualifies, and why these massive payouts happen..." canonical="https://westmountfundamentals.com/when-will-the-2000-dividend-be-paid" schema={JSON.stringify(schema)}>
